{"tid":1138833,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[東京] 由橫濱玩到山梨行程一問","createTime":"2019-05-04T19:15:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-05T05:41:57.000Z","uid":191556,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c1d6819fa25a0f4d01a4baa8c32ad73aece0934c","tid":1138833,"uid":191556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T19:15:52.000Z","msg":"黎緊會去12日東京, 想問下各位巴絲下面行程會唔會有D咩太趕/有D景點冇咩特別唔洗去咁, 同埋DAY4個日行程行唔行得通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>DAY1:</ins></strong> 落機 &gt; NEX 去橫濱 &gt; 酒店CHECK IN <br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>DAY2:</ins></strong> CHECK OUT &gt; 行李放酒店 &gt; 橫濱市內 &gt; 拉麵博物館 &gt; 橫濱紅磚倉庫 &gt; COSMO WORLD 橫濱摩天輪，三棟queen square及landmark tower &gt;橫濱車站旁的高島屋，Sogo，丸井，及地下街 &gt; 前往 沼津 (約1.5小時) &gt; CHECK IN 沼津酒店<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>DAY3:</ins></strong> 三島市內 &gt; SKY WALK 大吊橋 &gt; 大型展望小門 &gt; 深海水族館 <br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>DAY4:</ins></strong> CHECK OUT &gt; 搭JR 去御殿場 &gt; 搭SHUTTLE BUS去 OUTLET &gt;  搭巴士去河口湖 , 影影相 &gt; 搭巴士去甲府(山梨) <br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>DAY5後:</ins></strong> 山梨會大約玩2日左右, 之後應該會返返東京玩6-7日左右"},{"pid":"14231a652e5902d289200202b5060ed510dec3cf","tid":1138833,"uid":191556,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T05:13:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6fa9bffa8114849be828294e7d3852b455a0397","tid":1138833,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T05:41:57.000Z","msg":"第二日個行程趕到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />除非你全部門口影張相就走，否則一定去唔晒"}]}